<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.10.1">
<l>mañcāṭu varaiyēḻuṅ kaṭalka ḷēḻum vāṉakamum maṇṇakamum maṟṟu mellām</l>
<l>eñcāmal vayiṟṟaṭakki yāliṉ mēlō riḷantaḷiril kaṇvaḷarnta vīcaṉ ṟaṉṉai</l>
<l>tuñcānīr vaḷañcurakkum peṇṇait teṉpāl tūyanāṉma ṟaiyāḷar cōmuc ceyya</l>
<l>ceñcāli viḷaivayaluḷ tikaḻntu tōṉṟun tirukkōva lūrataṉuḷ kaṇṭēṉ nāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The lord who slept on a tender leaf on a banyan, concealing in his belly</l>
<l rend="indent">the seven mountains where mist stirs, the seven seas,</l>
<l>The space of the earth and the space of the sky,</l>
<l rend="indent">and all else without [anything] remaining,</l>
<l>I saw in Tirukkōvalūr which appears glittering in fields</l>
<l rend="indent">where the best paddy grows</l>
<l>On the southern shores of the Peṇṇai, which flows full of water, never failing,</l>
<l rend="indent">since experts in the four, pure Vedas make soma [offerings].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
